{"tid":2193832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國移除 1 萬多個「吃播」帳號 禁止浪費食物","createTime":"2020-09-08T06:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T07:56:30.000Z","uid":137088,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9394a82ada6af20bb1a294b6adb69bb2aea52225","tid":2193832,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/v2-bd166e014fe278410ce96e64e33b456e_1440w-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fv2-bd166e014fe278410ce96e64e33b456e_1440w-1.jpg&h=b8eaf588&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前中國的國家主席習近平表示要禁止浪費食物後，CCTV 點名批評「吃播」節目違規，繼而出現大批「吃播」帳號被下架，在一個月後已經有超過一萬個相關帳號被刪除。<br />\n<br />\n「吃播」文化源於韓國，主要是直播吃東西的節目，在中國也成為熱潮，彷彿形成一個產業鏈。這些節目通常以大胃王挑戰或者美女作招徠，吸引觀衆觀看。不過在最近習近平一聲令下之後，據稱已經有 1.36 萬個違規「吃播」帳號被刪除，甚至引發了吃播行業的失業潮。<br />\n<br />\n在最近的「三項整治」推進會中，中國中央網絡安全和信息化委員會辦公室表示，經過處置之後，「網絡傳播秩序明顯改觀，網絡生態有效改善，行業規範管理水平逐步提升。」未來他們將會繼續向違規網站平台、帳戶和主播施壓，營造「清朗健康的網絡空間」。"},{"pid":"fe11ac949cdc857d4b77a9b68acd4ab5ce0a3d9f","tid":2193832,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d230a8e0eaa24c6be2b115d0eb814a573944ce1","tid":2193832,"uid":372390,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DgKis1d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDgKis1d.png&h=194be722&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n直播食空氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06753b88f36559d15629b40aadac16d398cddec1","tid":2193832,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:37:04.000Z","msg":"抵啦，食到成隻豬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8961177b573a232103f2af82eb5386a895bbd27d","tid":2193832,"uid":122134,"like":2,"disli